README:

[1] Vorticity Thresholding:

        vorticity_abs_thresh <-- regrids when VORT > threshold value
        
        vorticity_rel_thresh <-- regrids when VORT > percent of max vorticity


[2] DOMAIN SIZE / RESOLUTION: Max resolution at finest level "512x512"

       --> MODIFIED FROM SQUARE GRID on [-1/2,1/2]x[-1/2,1/2], e.g., 

            CartesianGeometry {
                domain_boxes = [ (0,0),(N-1,N-1) ]
                x_lo = -.5*L,-.5*L
                x_up = .5*L,.5*L
                periodic_dimension = 1,1
            }
    
                                *** TO ***

            RECTANGULAR GRID on [-0.5,1.5]x[-0.25,0.25]

            CartesianGeometry {
                domain_boxes = [ (0,0),(2*N - 1,N/2 - 1) ]
                x_lo = -.5*L,-.25*L
                x_up = 1.0*L,.25*L
                periodic_dimension = 1,1
            }

      --> IN ORDER TO CHANGE THAT, WE MODIFIED THE PATCH SIZES:

            largest_patch_size {
                 // Originally set at 512,512
                 level_0 = 768,256  // all finer levels will use same values as level_0
            }
            smallest_patch_size {
                 // Originally set at 64,64
                 level_0 =  8,8 //48,16  // all finer levels will use same values as level_0
            }
        